20the%20moment%2C%20and%20offer%20live%20translations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20touted%20the%20new%20functions%20at%20Meta%20Connect%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20smart%20glasses%20are%20getting%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20tech%20behemoth%2C%20shared%20the%20updates%20to%20Meta's%20Ray-Bans%20during%20the%20company's%20annual%20show-and-tell%20conference%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-connect-live-updates-mark-zuckerberg-keynote-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20Connect%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20start%20to%20see%20how%20the%20future%20of%20computing%20and%20the%20future%20of%20human%20connection%20are%20going%20to%20look%2C%20and%20it's%20pretty%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said%2C%20touting%20Meta's%20smart%20glasses%2C%20mixed%20reality%2C%20and%20AI.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20love%20their%20Ray-Ban%20Meta%20glasses%20so%20much%20so%20that%20for%20a%20little%20while%2C%20we%20were%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20updated%20glasses%20will%20retain%20memories%20of%20what%20users%20see%20and%20remind%20them%20about%20it%20later%2C%20helping%20them%20remember%20things%20like%20what%20they%20need%20to%20buy%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20heading%20somewhere%2C%20no%20more%20forgetting%20where%20you%20parked.%20Your%20glasses%20have%20you%20covered%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20remind%20you%20to%20pick%20up%20some%20avocadoes%20at%20the%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20scan%20QR%20codes%2C%20include%20video%20functionality%20with%20Meta%20AI%20for%20better%20in-the-moment%20assistance%2C%20and%20have%20live%20language%20translations%20between%20English%20and%20French%2C%20Italian%2C%20and%20Spanish%20using%20AI%20automatic%20dubbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20adding%20multimodal%20video%20AI%2C%20so%20Meta%20AI%20is%20now%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20give%20you%20real-time%20help%20as%20you%20are%20doing%20things%2C%20like%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20outfit%20you%20want%20to%20wear%20for%20a%20party%20you%20are%20going%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20to%20build%20out%20over%20this%20to%20make%20it%20more%20useful%20over%20time%2C%20but%20this%20is%20gonna%20be%20a%20big%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%20will%20also%20include%20a%20new%20array%20of%20Transitions%20lenses%20from%20Ray-Ban%20maker%20EssilorLuxottica.%20The%20Ray-Ban%20Meta%20Wayfarer%20with%20polarized%20lenses%20costs%20%24329%2C%20while%20the%20Transitions%20options%20are%20%24379%2C%20according%20to%20Meta's%20website.%20There's%20also%20a%20limited%20edition%20transparent-framed%20pair%20of%20glasses%20available%20for%20%24429%20for%20customers%20who%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Bappreciate%20what%20makes%20them%20special%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20hiding%20the%20tech%20within%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20also%20just%20good-looking%20glasses.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20you're%20not%20using%20smart%20functionality%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20have%20something%20on%20their%20face%20that%20they're%20proud%20of%2C%20that%20looks%20good%2C%20that's%20designed%20in%20a%20very%20nice%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20existing%20models%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-ray-ban-smart-glasses-can-take-photos-and-calls-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERay-Ban%20Meta%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20let%20customers%20capture%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20live%20stream%20on%20Instagram%2C%20and%20accept%20video%20calls.%20The%20glasses%20have%20an%20LED%20light%20that%20emits%20a%20flash%20when%20a%20photo%20or%20video%20is%20taken%20to%20inform%20others%20nearby%20that%20they%20could%20be%20recorded.%20Still%2C%20users%20have%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-smart-glasses-ray-ban-light-recording-privacy-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etape%20over%20the%20light%20to%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20surreptitiously.%20Meta%20has%20said%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20its%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20September%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20announced%20it%20was%20adding%20Meta%20AI%20to%20its%20smart%20glasses%20for%20US-based%20customers%2C%20letting%20them%20use%20the%20virtual%20assistant%20AI%20with%20the%20command%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%20Meta.%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20touted%20this%20feature%20in%20an%20Instagram%20video%20where%20he%20used%20the%20AI%20to%20walk%20him%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-learns-braid-hair-meta-ray-ban-smart-glasses-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebraiding%20his%20daughter's%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Jordan%20Hart%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-ban-smart-glasses-gen-z-friends-review-photos-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etried%20out%20the%20smart%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20photo%20capture%20function%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20using%20a%20disposable%20camera%20thanks%20to%20the%20LED%20flash.%20Photos%20turned%20out%20dark%20in%20low-light%20settings%20and%20blurry%20even%20with%20better%20lighting.%20The%20lenses%20don't%20have%20an%20AR%20display%2C%20so%20images%20have%20to%20be%20reviewed%20using%20the%20Meta%20View%20app%20on%20a%20smartphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-bans-have-new-features-smart-glasses-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727290122000%2C%22visual%22%