0Wednesday%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-scale%20war%20is%20not%20in%20anyone's%20interest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael%20calls%20reservists%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECross-border%20clashes%20intensified%20Wednesday%20after%20Israeli%20raids%20on%20Monday%20killed%20at%20least%20558%20people%20in%20the%20deadliest%20day%20of%20violence%20in%20Lebanon%20since%20its%201975-90%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENour%20Hamad%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20student%20in%20the%20eastern%20Lebanese%20city%20of%20Baalbek%2C%20described%20living%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20state%20of%20terror%26quot%3B%20all%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20four%20or%20five%20days%20without%20sleep%2C%20not%20knowing%20if%20we%20will%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20sirens%20sounded%20following%20Hezbollah's%20unprecedented%20missile%20launch%20at%20dawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETel%20Aviv%20resident%20Hedva%20Fadlon%2C%2061%2C%20told%20AFP%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20difficult.%20We%20feel%20the%20pressure%20and%20the%20tension...%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20in%20the%20world%20would%20like%20to%20live%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20called%20Hezbollah's%20attack%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerning%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20added%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20time%20and%20space%20for%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20here%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20tensions%20and%20to%20prevent%20an%20all-out%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20%26quot%3Bover%20280%20Hezbollah%26quot%3B%20targets%20had%20been%20struck%20across%20Lebanon%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20added%20the%20strikes%20were%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFighter%20jets%20struck%2060%20terrorist%20targets%20belonging%20to%20Hezbollah's%20intelligence%20directorate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20army%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20two%20reserve%20brigades%20were%20being%20called%20up%20%26quot%3Bfor%20operational%20missions%20in%20the%20northern%20arena%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20this%20would%20%26quot%3Benable%20the%20continuation%20of%20combat%20against%20the%20Hezbollah%20terrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefiant%20Netanyahu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Security%20Council%20said%20it%20would%20hold%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20on%20the%20crisis%20in%20New%20York%20later%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20UN%20chief%20Antonio%20Guterres%20warned%20the%20situation%20was%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20all%20be%20alarmed%20by%20the%20escalation.%20Lebanon%20is%20at%20the%20brink%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN's%20International%20Organization%20for%20Migration%20on%20Wednesday%20said%2090%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20displaced%20in%20Lebanon%20so%20far%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20the%20more%20than%20111%2C000%20people%20displaced%20since%20October...%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20secondarily%20displaced%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20UN's%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20on%20Tuesday%20confirmed%20Israel%20had%20killed%20its%20rocket%20forces%20commander%20Ibrahim%20Kobeissi%20in%20a%20strike%20on%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20delayed%20his%20departure%20for%20New%20York%20until%20Thursday%2C%20where%20he%20too%20is%20due%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20General%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20premier%20has%20defied%20international%20calls%20for%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20hit%20Hezbollah...%20the%20one%20who%20has%20a%20missile%20in%20his%20living%20room%20and%20a%20rocket%20in%20his%20home%20will%20not%20have%20a%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20vowed%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%2C%20Hezboll