erstand%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20parent%20and%20have%20those%20delicate%20conversations%20with%20your%20family.%20Once%20you%20are%20clear%20about%20this%20decision%2C%20get%20the%20procedure%20done%20and%20move%20on%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Poonam%20notes%20that%20the%20discourse%20on%20the%20engagement%20of%20men%20as%20partners%20in%20accessing%20family%20planning%20and%20health%20services%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20contraceptive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMale%20participation%20is%20about%20being%20responsible%20and%20respecting%20equality%20rather%20than%20just%20about%20decision-making.%20It%20should%20extend%20to%20the%20role%20of%20men%20as%20enablers%20and%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ensuring%20dignity%2C%20equal%20voice%2C%20and%20reproductive%20rights%20for%20women.%20Male%20participation%20should%20not%20mean%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20decision-making%20powers%20are%20encumbered%2C%20and%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20accept%20men%E2%80%99s%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20that%20men%20often%20control%20contraception%20decision-making%20and%20decision%20of%20contraception%20of%20female%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20prevalence%20of%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20which%20can%20impede%20contraceptive%20use%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20risk%20for%20contraceptive%20failure.%20Male%20engagement%20in%20family%20planning%20should%20improve%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20health%20and%20promote%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727275238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Mumbai-based%20couple%20chose%20a%20vasectomy%20after%20deciding%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20breaking%20societal%20norms.%20Their%20decision%20came%20after%20extensive%20discussions%2C%20research%2C%20and%20consultations%20with%20doctors.%20Highlighting%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20societal%20challenges%2C%20they%20advocate%20for%20more%20men%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20family%20planning%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367509%2Fworld-contraception-day-why-more-indian-men-should-get-vasectomy-family-planning%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin's%20'Top%20Secret'%20Meet%20Over%20Nukes%20As%20Ukraine%20Plans%20Cruise%20Missile%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20called%20for%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20Moscow's%20top%20security%20council%20to%20discuss%20its%20nuclear%20deterrence.%20The%20move%20comes%20amid%20rising%20concerns%20in%20Russia%20over%20Ukraine%20being%20allowed%20by%20Western%20powers%20to%20use%20cruise%20missiles%20to%20target%20locations%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20UK%20reportedly%20cleared%20the%20use%20of%20its%20'Storm%20Shadow'%20cruise%20missile%20to%20be%20used%20to%20bomb%20Russia.%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20even%20flew%20to%20Washington%20DC%20to%20meet%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20two%20leaders%20reportedly%20discussed%20Ukraine's%20use%20of%20weapons%20on%20Russian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20intelligence%20had%20information%20about%20such%20a%20possibility%20and%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20necessary%20for%20Moscow%20to%20revise%20its%20nuclear%20doctrine%20because%20of%20the%20West's%20escalation%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fdvsfo8vg_storm-shadow-long-range-missiles_625x300_13_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesperson%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20that%20Mr%20Putin%20will%20meet%20the%20most%20powerful%20officials%20in%20his%20administration%20to%20discuss%20the%20war%20strategy%20going%20forward.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20speech%20by%20the%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Peskov%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20rest%2C%20for%20obvious%20reasons%2C%20will%20be%20marked%20'top%20secret'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20reports%20that%20the%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%20are%20about%20to%20give%20clearance%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20Kyiv%20to%20launch%20cruise%20missiles%20on%20Russian%20soil%2C%20President%20Putin%20said%20this%20month%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20West%20would%20be%20directly%20fighting%20with%20Russia%20if%20it%20gave%20such%20permission%20to%20Ukraine%20(to%20bomb%20Russia)%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20Moscow%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20decisions%26quot%3B%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERUSSIA'S%20NUCLEAR%20DOCTRINE%20%26amp%3B%20TREATY%20WITH%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20nuclear%20power.%20Together%2C%20Russia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20control%2088%25%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20current%20nuclear%20doctrine%20was%20set%20in%20place%20by%20Vladimir%20Putin%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20before%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out.%20According%20to%20the%20current%20doctrine%2C%20Russia%20may%20use%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20the%20scenario%20where%20it%20comes%20under%20a%20nuclear%20attack%20or%20if%20a%20conventional%20attack%20threatens%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fim09u9j8_russian-yars-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-system-reuters_625x300_25_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%2C%20who%20is%20the%20primary%20decision%20maker%20on%20Russia's%20massive%20nuclear%20arsenal%2C%20is%20now%20planning%20how%20to%20respond%20if%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20European%20allies%20allow%20Ukraine%20to%20use%20Western-supplied%20missiles%20to%20strike%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20have%20a%20nuclear%20treaty%20called%20the%20US-Russia%20New%20START%20Treaty%2C%20which%20entered%20into%20force%20on%20February%205%2C%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20treaty%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20had%20seven%20years%20to%20meet%20the%20treaty's%20central%20limits%20on%20strategic%20offensive%20arms%20(by%20February%205%2C%202018)%20and%20are%20then%20obligated%20to%20maintain%20those%20limits%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20treaty%20remains%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department%2C%20this%20treaty%20enhances%20US%20national%20security%20by%20placing%20verifiable%20limits%20on%20all%20Russian%20deployed%20intercontinental-range%20nuclear%20weapons.%20The%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20have%20agreed%20to%20extend%20the%20treaty%20through%20February%204%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%