0the%20latter%20is%20its%20first%20domestically%20built%20carrier.%20The%20third%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20Fujian%2C%20is%20China's%20largest%20and%20most%20advanced%20aircraft%20carrier%20ever%20built%20with%20a%20potent%20aircraft%20launching%20system.%20Fujian%20underwent%20sea%20trials%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20commissioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Global%20Times%2C%20the%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%2C%20reported%2C%20that%20China's%20aircraft%20carrier%20program%20has%20entered%20a%20fast%20lane.%20The%20Liaoning%20aircraft%20carrier%20conducted%20routine%20exercises%20in%20water%20including%20the%20West%20Pacific%2C%20to%20enhance%20combat%20capabilities%2C%20Senior%20Colonel%20Zhang%20Xiaogang%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Ministry%20of%20National%20Defense%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20carrier%20follows%20a%20deployment%20cycle%2C%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20which%20is%20spent%20on%20the%20station.%20When%20not%20on%20station%2C%20the%20ship%20is%20in%20one%20of%20three%20other%20phases%3A%20in%20transit%20to%20or%20from%20the%20operating%20area%2C%20in%20its%20home%20port%20for%20maintenance%2C%20crew%20rest%2C%20and%20shore%20training%20or%20at%20sea%20for%20short%20periods%20of%20crew%20training%20or%20operations%20when%20not%20deployed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20conventionally%20powered%20and%20nuclear-powered%20carriers%20undergo%20several%20deployment%20cycles%20within%20one%20operating%20cycle%2C%20which%20is%20the%20time%20between%20complex%20overhauls%20(periods%20of%20major%20maintenance).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%20001%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Liaoning%20aircraft%20carrier%20(Type%20001)%20was%20spotted%20north%20of%20Taiwan%20and%20near%20Japan.%20The%20Japanese%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20said%20they%20detected%20the%20Chinese%20navy's%20movement%20in%20its%20economic%20waters%20-%20a%20maritime%20area%20that%20extends%20200%20nautical%20miles%20beyond%20its%20terr