ing%20in%20the%20Julana%20constituency%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hereby%20given%20a%20formal%20notice%20to%20notify%20you%20about%20apparent%20failure%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20whereabouts%20requirements%20of%20the%20ADR%2C%20and%20to%20invite%20you%20to%20make%20any%20comments%20before%20we%20come%20to%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NADA%20notice%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Dope%20Control%20Officer%20(DCO)%20was%20sent%20to%20test%20you%20on%20that%20dav%20at%20that%20time%20and%20place.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20locate%20you%20for%20testing%20as%20you%20were%20not%20available%20at%20the%20given%20location.%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20needs%20to%20either%20accept%20the%20failure%20or%20provide%20evidence%20that%20she%20was%20present%20in%20that%20location%20for%20about%2060%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20mentioned%20that%20one%20whereabouts%20failure%20does%20not%20constitute%20an%20anti-doping%20rule%20violation.%20There%20must%20be%20three%20whereabouts%20failures%20(whether%20filing%20failures%20or%20missed%20tests)%20within%20a%2012-month%20period%20for%20NADA%20to%20charge%20an%20athlete.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727273520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F6uvtt19o_vinesh-phogat_625x300_22_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fvinesh-phogat-gets-notice-from-national-anti-doping-body-for-apparent-failure-to-comply-with-6648247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20had%20announced%20her%20retirement%20from%20the%20sport%20after%20her%20Paris%20Olympics%20campaign%20ended%20in%20heartbreak%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F