y%20transferred%2C%20within%20a%20timeline%20of%20just%2015%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20floods.%20This%20is%20the%20fastest%20timeline%20for%20compensation%20disbursement%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20successfully%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20state%20government%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20when%20the%20previous%20government%20led%20by%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20managed%20the%20compensation%20process%20for%20Michuang%20cyclone%2C%20which%20struck%20on%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20compensation%20of%20Rs%20442%20crores%20was%20disbursed%20on%20May%2017%2C%202024%2C%20or%20over%20five%20months%20since%20the%20natural%20disaster%20struck.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20we%20were%20motivated%20to%20provide%20immediate%20and%20sufficient%20compensation.%20Our%20Chief%20Minister%20led%20by%20example%20during%20the%20relief%20efforts.%20We%20are%20happy%20about%20this%20unprecedented%20speed%20in%20disbursing%20the%20compensation%20amounts.%20We%20hope%20our%20efforts%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20successful%20template%20for%20future%20disaster%20management%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RP%20Sisodia%2C%20Special%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Revenue).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727273040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fovrksemg_chandrababu-naidu_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fandhra-claims-rs-600-crore-flood-compensation-paid-in-record-time-10-points-6648264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20gave%20Rs%20602%20crore%20compensation%20to%20four%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20in%20a%20record%20time%20of%2015%20days%20using%20technology-driven%20interventions%2C%20the%20government%20said.%20Vijayawada%20and%20surrounding%20areas%20were%20struck%20by%20floods%20in%20September.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22