angana%20Ranaut%20issued%20a%20public%20apology%20and%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bregret%26quot%3B%20over%20her%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandi%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20had%20suggested%20that%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20that%20were%20repealed%20following%20prolonged%20farmer%20protests%20should%20be%20brought%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor-turned-politician%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20statement%20could%20be%20controversial%2C%20but%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20should%20be%20brought%20back.%20Farmers%20themselves%20should%20demand%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20BJP%20stated%20that%20her%20comments%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20authorised%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ranaut%20retracted%20her%20remarks%20and%20issued%20an%20apology.%20She%20added%20that%20moving%20forward%2C%20she%20will%20ensure%20her%20views%20align%20with%20the%20party's%20stance%20rather%20than%20representing%20her%20personal%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Jaiveer%20Shergill%20further%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20bond%20with%20Punjab%2C%20the%20farmers%20of%20Punjab%20and%20%26quot%3BPunjabiyat%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20unbreakable%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20said%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20doubt%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20bond%20with%20Punjab%2C%20the%20farmer%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Punjabiyat%20is%20an%20unbreakable%2C%20unshakable%20bond%20and%20that%20bond%20should%20not%20be%20judged%20or%20seen%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20irresponsible%20comments%20being%20made%20by%20one%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20national%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20BJP%20Spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20has%20said%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20remarks%20are%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20statements%26quot%3B%20and%20don't%20depict%20the%20BJP's%20view%20on%20farm%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20social%20media%20platfor