0but%20also%20uplift%20agriculture%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReturning%20to%20his%20roots%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20revive%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20farming%20legacy%20by%20focusing%20on%20cultivating%20moringa%20oleifera%20%E2%80%94%20a%20versatile%20tree%20known%20for%20its%20nutritional%20and%20medicinal%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERedefining%20moringa%20farming%20with%20sustainable%20practices%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20difference%20between%20farming%20techniques%20for%20harvesting%20drumsticks%20and%20leaves%2C%20Dr%20Saravanan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20drumstick%20farming%2C%20trees%20are%20planted%20with%20a%20wider%20spacing%20of%2015%20feet%2C%20whereas%20in%20its%20leaves%20cultivation%2C%20saplings%20are%20planted%20closely%20together.%20The%20leaves%20are%20cut%20when%20the%20tree%20reaches%20a%20height%20of%20two%20feet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20allow%20the%20tree%20to%20flower%2C%20the%20nutrition%20stored%20in%20the%20leaves%20will%20be%20used%20up%20to%20grow%20the%20drumsticks.%20This%20will%20result%20in%20lesser-quality%20leaves.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20harvest%20the%20leaves%20before%20the%20flowering%20phase.%20Also%2C%20you%20can%20harvest%20leaves%20up%20to%20six%20times%20at%2050%20to%2060%20day%20intervals.%20This%20ensures%20year-round%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saravanan%20uses%20no-till%20cultivation%20to%20grow%20the%20moringa%20leaves.%20He%20implements%20organic%20farming%20practices%20using%20goat%20manure%20and%20farmyard%20waste.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20has%20also%20installed%20drip%20irrigation%20to%20ensure%20crops%20are%20grown%20without%20any%20wastage.%20To%20maximise%20production%20and%20suppress%20weed%20growth%2C%20he%20uses%20a%20new%20technique%20called%20bundle%20mulching%2C%20where%20crop%20residues%2C%20such%20as%20dry%20leaves%20are%20stacked%20along%20the%20crop%20rows%20to%20suppress%20weed%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Saravanan%20processes%20leaves%20into%20value-added%20products%20such%20as%20moringa%20podi%20and%20leaf%20soup.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-3-1727091806-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Saravanan%20processes%20leaves%20into%20value-added%20products%20such%20as%20moringa%20%3Cem%3Epodi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20leaf%20soup.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20conventional%20mulching%20methods%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20control%20weed%20growth.%20Its%20impact%20hardly%20lasted%20for%20two%20months.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20weed%20started%20growing%20again%2C%20so%20the%20major%20problem%20for%20which%20the%20mulching%20is%20done%20was%20not%20taken%20care%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccidentally%2C%20I%20had%20put%20a%20one-foot%20bundle%20of%20leaves%20along%20three%20rows%20in%20the%20field.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20I%20found%20it%20was%20very%20effective%20in%20checking%20weed%20growth.%20This%20controlled%20the%20weed%20growth%20for%20six%20t