ment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20happy%20now%20and%20at%20peace%20within%20myself.%20Initially%2C%20I%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20struggles%20as%20I%20had%20to%20invest%20almost%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20cultivating%20the%20farm.%20But%20now%20I%20am%20getting%20the%20fruits%20of%20my%20struggles.%20I%20went%20against%20my%20family%20when%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20at%20the%20university%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20you%20really%20do%20what%20you%20love%2C%20you%20feel%20rewarded%20at%20the%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Kandasami%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727094333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmoringa-1-1727091716.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20drumstick%20farming%20became%20unprofitable%20due%20to%20low%20market%20rates%2C%20Dr%20Kandasami%20Saravanan%20turned%20to%20harvesting%20the%20leaves%20instead.%20He%20launched%20a%20successful%20venture%20selling%20value-added%20products%20like%20moringa%20podi%2C%20leaf%20soup%2C%20and%20powder%20across%20the%20USA%2C%20Canada%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Gulf%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shell%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Changemakers%20of%20Tomorrow%202024%E2%80%99%3A%20Revolutionary%20Ideas%2C%20From%20Seed%20Sowing%20Shoes%20to%20Biofuel%20Robots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Shell%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20sharing%20your%20groundbreaking%20ideas%20on%20a%20Shark%20Tank-style%20pitching%20stage%2C%20with%20just%20five%20minutes%20to%20impress%20the%20judges.%20Sounds%20like%20a%20dream%2C%20right%3F%20Well%2C%20that%20drea