0Sankar%20has%20been%20the%20recipient%20of%20numerous%20national%20and%20international%20accolades%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Puraskar%20in%202016%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Puraskar%20in%202016%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20rural%20credit%20accounted%20for%20only%2020.8%20percent%20(Rs%2011.99%20lakh%20crore)%20of%20the%20Rs%2057.58%20lakh%20crore%20sanctioned%20by%20NBFCs%20in%202021.%20This%20highlights%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%20in%20access%20to%20credit.%20Thus%2C%20when%20designing%20a%20blueprint%20for%20the%20job%20creation%20model%2C%20Dr%20Sankar%20says%20facilitating%20access%20to%20economic%20capital%20was%20prime.%20She%20decided%20to%20keep%20financial%20independence%20for%20women%20at%20the%20fore.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%