this%20irreparable%20loss%20was%20heart-wrenching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20196px)%20100vw%2C%20196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjunath%20with%20his%20friend%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841.jpeg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841-150x230.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366859%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManjunath%20with%20his%20friend%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20mother%20made%20a%20statement%20on%20TV%20that%20echoed%20across%20the%20country%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20crying%20tears%20of%20blood.%20What%20can%20we%20(husband%20and%20wife)%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helplessness%20of%20the%20common%20people%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20harsh%20system%20was%20painfully%20evident.%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20were%20unable%20to%20forget%20Manjunath%20or%20what%20his%20mother%20had%20said.%20It%20was%20time%20for%20action.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20his%20parents%20may%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331304%2Fdevanshi-yadav-shaheed-ramashray-welfare-society-bareilly-acid-attack-sexual-abuse-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20the%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%2C%20as%20a%20community%20of%20IIM%20professionals%2C%20could.%20We%20decided%20to%20harness%20this%20collective%20power%20for%20good%2C%E2%