%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20thing%20necessary%20for%20the%20triumph%20of%20evil%C2%A0%20is%20for%20good%20men%20to%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20ethical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20directly%20paying%20bribes%2C%20many%20of%20us%20hire%20agents%20or%20brokers%20who%20do%20it%20on%20our%20behalf.%20Anjali%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20go%20out%20of%20your%20way%20to%20bribe.%20If%20you%20break%20a%20traffic%20signal%2C%20pay%20the%20fine%2C%20not%20the%20cop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelp%20those%20in%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20our%20responsibility%20to%20create%20a%20more%20equitable%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20up%20to%20those%20who%20are%20more%20privileged%2C%20focus%20on%20the%20millions%20living%20in%20poverty%20and%20do%20your%20part%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20small%20contribution%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Give%20whatever%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Rs%201%2C000%20or%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20your%20own%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20remain%20modest%20about%20their%20efforts%2C%20the%20Shanmugam%20family%20is%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20for%20us.%20God%20comes%20in%20different%20forms.%20Everyone%20who%20came%20forward%20to%20help%2C%20motivate%2C%20and%20console%20us%2C%20including%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20friends%20and%20juniors%2C%20were%20manifestations%20of%20God.%20They%20showed%20me%20that%20there%20are%20good%20people%20in%20society%2C%20to%20balance%20out%20the%20bad%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raghavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20showed%20the%20country%20that%20all%20it%20takes%20is%20for%20one%20person%20to%20take%20charge%20and%20act.%20Instead%20of%20merely%20making%20this%20case%20a%20dinner%20table%20conversation%2C%20they%20went%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20fought.%20All%20it%20takes%20is%20that%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20be%20your%20first%20step%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Raghavendra%20Shanmugam%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726842542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1-1726828603.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20IOC%20officer%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20was%20murdered%20for%20exposing%20petrol%20adulteration%2C%20his%20IIM%20alumni%2C%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20refused%20to%20stay%20silent.%20Taking%20action%20into%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20they%20fought%20a%20relentless%20legal%20battle%2C%20ensuring%20all%20the%20accused%20were%20convicted%20and%20justice%20was%20served.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366845%2Fmanjunath-shanmugam-kolar-lakhimpur-kheri-karnataka-uttar-pradesh-anjali-mullatti-jaishankar-iim-ioc-murder-justice-whistleblower-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Truck%20Driver%E2%80%99s%20Daughter%20to%20Cannes%3A%20How%20Sunita%20Rajwar%20Brought%20Her%20Father%E2%80%99s%20Cinema%20Dreams%20to%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20remember%20Sunita%20Rajwar%20for%20her%20recent%20role%20in%20%3Cem%3EStree%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20Janna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20or%20as%20the%20strong-willed%20Kranti%20Devi%20in%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20on%20the%20road%20to%20stardom%2C%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20glitz%20and%20glamour%20of%20the%20entertainment%20world%20lighting%20her%20way.%20Instead%2C%20all%20she%20carried%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Egullak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(piggy%20bank)%20full%20of%20dreams%2C%20determination%2C%20and%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Haldwani%2C%20a%20small%20town%20nestled%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20her%20early%20life%20was%20far%20from%20the%20spotlight.%20Her%20father%2C%20a%20truck%20driver%2C%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20provide%20for%20the%20family%2C%20and%20it%20was%20his%20love%20for%20cinema%20that%20planted%20the%20first%20seeds%20of%20acting%20in%20young%20Sunita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20years%2C%20I%20was%20hesitant%20to%20discuss%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunita%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%E2%80%99ve%20grown%20to%20understand%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20to%20be%20proud%20of%2C%20not%20ashamed%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20financial%20struggles%2C%20her%20father%20made%20sure%20that%20his%20children%20received%20the%20best%20education%20possible%2C%20often%20taking%20the%20family%20to%20theatre%20performances%20every%20Friday.%20This%20routine%20became%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20igniting%20Sunita%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20drama%20and%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8cU6r2o-Xo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8cU6r2o-Xo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20