0to%20question%20her%20future%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20fate%20intervened.%20A%20call%20for%20an%20audition%20led%20her%20to%20the%20role%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBittu%20ki%20mummy%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20series%20became%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20with%20audiences%20praising%20Sunita%E2%80%99s%20impeccable%20portrayal%20of%20the%20nosy%2C%20hilarious%20neighbour.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20this%2C%20I%20used%20to%20do%20small%20roles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20found%20out%20about%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%E2%80%99s%20film%20career%20began%20with%20roles%20in%20%3Cem%3EEk%20Chalis%20Ki%20Last%20Local%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20later%20included%20critically%20acclaimed%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EStree%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EKedarnath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EShubh%20Mangal%20Savdhan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20it%20was%20her%20breakthrough%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20that%20truly%20elevated%20her%20career%2C%20with%20her%20memorable%20performances%20in%20%3Cem%3EGullak%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20catapulting%20her%20to%20stardom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20reached%20new%20heights%20when%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F185859%2Fcannes-film-festival-meghalaya-india-dominic-sangma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalked%20the%20red%20carpet%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20representing%20her%20film%20%3Cem%3ESantosh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20For%20the%20small-town%20girl%20who%20once%20shared%20dingy%20rooms%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Sunita%20inspires%20many%2C%20as%20her%20%3Cem%3Egullak%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20dreams%20has%20finally%20cracked%20open%2C%20with%20one%20dream%20materialising%20after%20another!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E