l%20winner%20of%20the%20prestigious%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplauding%20the%20ingenious%20tricks%20her%20friends%20devised%20to%20prolong%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20insulin%20while%20travelling%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20them%20stores%20the%20vial%20in%20a%20thermos%20flask%2C%20while%20the%20other%2C%20who%20lives%20down%20South%20and%20makes%2027-hour-long%20train%20trips%20back%20home%2C%20purchases%20a%20chilled%20bottle%20of%20water%20at%20every%20station%20in%20which%20she%20then%20places%20the%20vial.%E2%80%9D%20Think%20of%20it%20like%20a%20mini-fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClever%20as%20these%20innovations%20are%2C%20it%20baffled%20Komal%20how%20no%20one%20was%20finding%20the%20process%20cumbersome.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20had%20to%20be%20a%20simpler%20solution%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20caught%20herself%20thinking%20this%20during%20one%20%E2%80%98Technically%20Complex%20Project%E2%80%99%20lecture%20in%20her%20second%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSPLrsJewqrA%3Fsi%3DPCV60HkUE2dY60Av%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Komal%2C%20this%20need%20to%20ideate%20stemmed%20from%20personal%20sentiment.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20watched%20my%20father%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266427%2Fmiracle-millets-diabetes-indian-food-recipes-weight-loss-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggle%20with%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20I%20was%20little.%20He%20would%20rush%20home%20every%20afternoon%20from%20his%20job%20in%20a%20steel%20factory%2C%20just%20so%20he%20could%20take%20his%20insulin%20shot.%20The%20factory%20does%20not%20have%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20ice%20packs%20prove%20impractic